name: christmas gift
description:
Merry Christmas to all my METAVERSE FAM, frens, collaborators and collectors, thank you for believe in me and my art, for your support as an artist and as a person, I´m truly greatful for this passed month, you all had been, for sure,  the highlight of my year.

Thank you for believe in me.

Love you all, merry christmas, happy holidays and a wondeful 2022, I wish you all everything ypur hearts desire.
